                    <p>1, 2, 5, 6(1), 6(3)(a, (c) and (f), 6(4)(a), (c), and (d), 6(8)(a), (c)(i) and (e)(i), 6(9)(j)(ii), 6(11)(a) to (c), 6(13)(a), 8 to 11</p>
